        <headline>Severe Thunderstorm Warning issued July 8 at 11:40PM CDT until July 9 at 12:00AM CDT by NWS Amarillo TX</headline>
        <description>At 1139 PM CDT, a severe thunderstorm was located 6 miles southwest
of Gruver, or 15 miles west of Spearman, moving west at 10 mph.

HAZARD...70 mph wind gusts and quarter size hail.

SOURCE...Radar indicated.

IMPACT...Expect some tree damage. Damage is likely to mobile homes,
roofs, and outbuildings. Hail damage to vehicles is
expected.

Locations impacted include...
Gruver.
</description>
        <instruction>For your protection move to an interior room on the lowest floor of a
building.</instruction>
